---
const title = "djerhy.tech";
const description = "Asset intelligence is not inventory. It is operational understanding.";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content={description}>

  <meta property="og:title" content={title}>
  <meta property="og:description" content={description}>
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">

  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #0D1117;
      --text: #e6edf3;
      --muted: #b1bac4;   /* brighter than before for readability */
      --muted2: #9aa4af;  /* secondary muted */
      --border: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.12);
      --border2: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.08);
      --panel: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.03);
      --panel2: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.05);
      --primary: #2F81F7;
      --primaryHover: #1E6AD8;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Header */
    header {
      margin-bottom: 64px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 650;
      color: var(--text);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    nav a {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* Hero */
    main {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .hero {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(34px, 6vw, 54px);
      line-height: 1.08;
      font-weight: 750;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    .hero-note {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--muted2);
      max-width: 640px;
    }

    /* Sections */
    .section {
      margin-top: 36px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted2);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .bullets li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.04);
    }

    .bullets li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.35);
      margin-top: 10px;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    /* Typical situation card */
    .card {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .card p + p {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* CTAs */
    .ctas {
      margin-top: 36px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .cta-primary {
      display: block;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 22px 22px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.06s;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .cta-primary:hover {
      background: var(--primaryHover);
    }

    .cta-primary:active {
      transform: translateY(1px);
    }

    .cta-primary-title {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .cta-primary-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      opacity: 0.95;
      font-weight: 450;
    }

    .cta-secondary {
      display: block;
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s, transform 0.06s;
    }

    .cta-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--panel2);
      border-color: rgba(230, 237, 243, 0.16);
    }

    .cta-secondary:active {
      transform: translateY(1px);
    }

    .cta-secondary-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .cta-secondary-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      padding-top: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted2);
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .footer-identity {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .container {
        padding: 32px 16px;
      }

      header {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .hero-sub {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="logo">djerhy.tech</a>
      <nav>
        <a href="/start-here">Start Here</a>
        <a href="/resources">Field Notes</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>Asset intelligence is not inventory.<br>It is operational understanding.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          Address The Mess maps ownership and decision authority so organizations can act, not just monitor.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-note">
          The process is designed to be run on one system over about four weeks.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title">This helps if</div>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li><span class="dot"></span><span>Upgrades keep getting delayed because dependencies are unclear.</span></li>
          <li><span class="dot"></span><span>Nobody can confidently approve a change.</span></li>
          <li><span class="dot"></span><span>Systems exist but ownership is uncertain.</span></li>
          <li><span class="dot"></span><span>Audits trigger last minute investigation.</span></li>
          <li><span class="dot"></span><span>Inherited infrastructure makes every change feel risky.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="section-title">Typical situation</div>
        <div class="card">
          <p>An organization believed they had a performance issue.</p>
          <p>Several legacy services and vendors were present, but no one could confirm what could be safely disconnected.</p>
          <p>The problem was not bandwidth. The problem was decision authority.</p>
          <p>Once ownership and dependencies were mapped, safe changes became possible.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="ctas">
        <a href="/start-here" class="cta-primary">
          <div class="cta-primary-title">Run the Operational Checks</div>
          <div class="cta-primary-desc">Start here. Confirm whether a clarity problem exists.</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources" class="cta-secondary">
          <div class="cta-secondary-title">Address The Mess</div>
          <div class="cta-secondary-desc">Overview and supporting materials for running the 30 day process.</div>
        </a>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="footer-identity">Djerhy Jn Baptiste • CISSP</div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/djerhyjnbaptiste" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/JBDjerhy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
        <a href="https://www.credly.com/users/djerhy-jn-baptiste" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Credly</a>
      </div>
      <div>© 2026 djerhy.tech</div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
